T1  - Helping and Voice Extra-Role Behaviors: Evidence of Construct and Predictive Validity
AU  - Van Dyne, Linn
AU  - LePine, Jeffrey A.
Y1  - 1998/02/01
PY  - 1998
DA  - 1998/02/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/256902
